title: Max Lobovsky says 3D Printing is more than just the machine
text:
Max Lobovsky says 3D Printing is more than just the machine 26 October 2015 Expand Formlabs ' co-founder and CEO, Max Lobovsky introduces the Form 2 at the TCT Show + Personalize 2015 Conference and shares his experiences on starting out in the 3D printing industry and what he hopes the next phase of the technology will bring. 
Find out more about the Form 2 in our video interview with Max at TCT Show here . 
To keep up-to-date on all the latest videos from TCT Show make sure you subscribe to our YouTube channel . Tags
